name: Commutes #2c
description:
Radiant glow infused it with strange shadows
the flame carved notches and lines upon the walls
while the shadows wafted up
as if the flame
fused with the walls

Digital & Acrylic on paper
1479x1600 px


A collection of digital hand drawings while commuting to work. This is done mostly in my android phone. Falling down the rabbit hole of one's self and looking at people.
